# mdatp-quick-scan-runner
# Example cron configuration

# Run quick scan daily at 2:00 AM
0 2 * * * /usr/local/bin/mdatp-quick-scan-runner/run.sh >> /var/log/microsoft/cron_mdatp_quick_scan.log 2>&1

Notes:
- Redirects stdout/stderr to a separate cron log
- Keeps native tool log (mdatp_quick_scan.log) intact
- Suitable for standalone or lightly managed systems
